{"tid":1527534,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"好多坪洲居民去東涌玩","createTime":"2019-09-01T10:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T10:53:59.000Z","uid":280827,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f72a61e38fc632dfbd12a6d7b566d8531a3c33d","tid":1527534,"uid":280827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"見最近大家都好有興趣去離島玩<br />\n想建議個新路線<br />\n東涌有巴士去愉景灣 好多人會選擇直出中環或者梅窩<br />\n其實巴士站再行前少少有街渡去坪洲<br />\n而坪洲作為一個冇咩人嘅小島 有個缺點就係冇重案組同冇咩警察 擔心治安嘅朋友仔就唔好去啦 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e5dcff2f11117309a47754b497a12f0eec6ea4","tid":1527534,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488bf58a373f960822550bda0a6352705734a059","tid":1527534,"uid":280827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"另外 坪洲好多公園同海邊無咩人 大家想靜靜地坐下都可以<br />\n晚上都有餐廳開 食下野享受小島風情<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf231f5cec90d770ab6c4483e866156bd6bbf79b","tid":1527534,"uid":308377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2c80763526493f3347123349469606206c0d69","tid":1527534,"uid":280827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf231f5cec90d770ab6c4483e866156bd6bbf79b","tid":1527534,"uid":308377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB